"{\"uid\": \"myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com-news-nepal-triathlon-association-organizes-triathlon-on-olympic-day-2024\", \"text\": \"Subscribe Now  KATHMANDU, June 16: The Nepal Triathlon Association\\u00a0 organized 'NTA Masters Triathlon' competition to celebrate Olympic Day 2024 on Saturday.  Jamieson and Anna Tyndall emerged as champions in the competition. Jamieson secured first place in the men's category, followed by Gayle Wasmer in second place and Ross White in third.  In the women's event, Anna Tyndall claimed victory, with Sonya Martin and Catherine taking second and third places, respectively.  In the team category, the group comprising Tika Jirel, Narayan Thapa, and Ash Narayan Chaudhary emerged as winners.  The team of Samir Shrestha, Karma Gurung, and Jane Bajracharya secured second place, while the team of Ayush Maharjan, Pradeep Nepal, and Surya Maharjan stood third.  The triathlon, which started at Tushal Multivenue in Manmaiju and concluded at Manmaiju Dya Chhen, included a 250m swim, a five-kilometer cycling segment, and a two-kilometer run.    Ballot Box Revolt: What RSP's breakthrough victory...  Warning, Threat or Opportunity? Nepal's major part...  Granary in crisis: Water politics leave Madhesh pa...  \\\"China stands ready to work with Nepal to carry forward the traditional friendship, deepen practical cooperation and advance bilateral relations\\\", read the statement.  Building Nepal's Digital Future  Fuel shortages in Nepal: A hidden threat to health a...  Second Innings of Balen and Gagan  Who will become Balen's climate pilot?  Three \\\"S\\\" factors-sulabhata (availability), sangat (peer influence), and siko (imitation)-are driving Madhesh's youth toward drug addiction.<...  Three \\\"S\\\" factors-sulabhata (availability), sangat (peer influence), and siko (imitation)-are driving Madhesh's youth toward drug addiction.<...  ANFA CEO Indraman Tuladhar said the ANFA submitted all necessary documents regarding foreign players' visas to t